有消息了。 我去哪里不知道啊，我什么时候回 EDG 了？，EDG 明年应该是 5 个 5 个新人吧，我只能说应该是 5 个新人，肯定没有 jiejie 呀，赵礼杰今年我和他基本上我和他就是知道摆烂最晚的，我跟他是最晚知道摆烂的， 就转会期都结束了，我们才知道田野走了，我跟他是最后知道，我们要跟三个新人一起打呀，一开始不是这样听说，一开始知道好像是要买一些人的。但最后知道，我们是要跟三个新人一起打，然后目标是进个季后赛， 对啊现在俱乐部基本都那个赛季结束，都把那个选手选手合同结了，就是不发工资 都在节约成本，好多俱乐部现在都干这种事，这事应该有很多人知道了，确实是 LPL 选手工资比其他行业高高高的，有点太多了，现在修整一下感觉也也是合理的。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8f5568c1580acc46027b1de0e2155e77_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1808703397"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIwtrwwPCexedYEAMaCTExMTMzODMxOSD/3OK4BjAAODRACnIKMTgwODcwMzM5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1729730807.371680", "card_id": "Q_1559953472", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "领导一般会如何看待那些不争不抢、闷声干活且业绩不错的员工？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1b4b8033096f23ec0752a031fe5ffcfd_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1559953472"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIwtrwwPCexedYEAMaCTExMTI4ODc2MCDpmte4BjAAONQBQAtyCjE1NTk5NTM0NzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1729730807.372316", "card_id": "Q_667767788", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specif